{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is the Digital Art Book of DREAMERS adventure game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With its charismatic trio of characters, vibrant low-poly graphics, and captivating soundtrack, the game warmed the hearts of lovers of cozy adventures and nostalgic players of all ages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841810/extras/DREAMERS_Bundle_Digital_Art_Book.gif?t=1730375899\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Today, this special edition invites you into the creative process with concept art, in-editor screenshots, and insights from the development team, including glimpses into the backstory ideas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This digital experience brings an extra value to the hardcover art book we published in December 2023, because it allows you to immerse yourself in a peaceful walking exploration through the game's initial location, offering a perspective never seen before in the game \u2014 through the eyes of one of its protagonists.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">COLLECTOR HARDCOPY EDITION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you want to add the hardcover copy to your collection, the art book is also available in a limited 300-page edition on the game's website.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841810/extras/DREAMERS_Bundle_Collector_Art_Book.gif?t=1730375899\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841810/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730375899","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841810/page.bg.jpg?t=1730375899","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841810/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730375899",